introduction_text: Thanks for your interest! Please take a few moments to fill this form. The better you tell us who you are, the better chances are that we want to have you in our team.
name: join-us
success_message: Thanks for applying. If we find your profile interesting, we will get back to you. In the mean-time you can always edit your application.
title: Join Us

web_form_fields.description: Not what your friends call you
web_form_fields.label: Full Name

web_form_fields.description: An email id you check frequently
web_form_fields.label: Email Id

web_form_fields.description: Want to share a resume? Link to a document via Dropbox or other similar file sharing tools
web_form_fields.label: Linked In Profile

web_form_fields.description: Already on GitHub / Bitbucket / Dribbble? Do you blog? Yay! Share your profile.
web_form_fields.label: GitHub Profile

web_form_fields.description: Tell us about your interests, your influences, what do you do in your free time.
web_form_fields.label: What are you passionate about?

web_form_fields.description: Your past is the best pointer to your future. Share your achievements, like what is the toughest thing you have done? What is your superpower? Any pet projects?
web_form_fields.label: What have you done till now?

web_form_fields.description: Yes we know everyone needs a job, but why us? Go through our website and find what interests you. Why do you think working with us is the best decision you will ever make.
web_form_fields.label: Why Us

web_form_fields.options:
Website
Industry
Country Specific
Accounting
Integration
General
Tools

web_form_fields.description: GitHub / Bitbucket etc link to the repository
